sources.title: Paranormal Abduction | Full Thriller Movie
sources.description:
***This film is under license from ITN Distribution. All rights reserved.***

Paranormal Abduction - A young women suffering memory loss and psychological issues after surviving a brutal attack, tries to piece together the clues surrounding her attack and its similarities to a series of recent murders. During the investigation, she struggles to maintain her sanity as her world gets more surreal and reality starts to unwind around her. Following the clues that lead her down the "rabbit hole" she finds herself fighting to wake up from this nightmare...before she becomes the next victim.

2012
Stars: Edward Furlong, Vail Bloom, Heather McComb
